				<td colspan="2"><span>I am a bard that solo's much more than I group due to limited playing time.  I'm curious how much Rizlona's fire is necessary as compared to other options.  Is it FABULOUS... or is it just nice to have at times... My other option would be to use those points to purchase Gravestone of Dire Melodies and put it on something so I didn't have to switch instruments when charm kiting.  Just curious as to your imput.
