End result? 
<br />

<br />
I memed Rizlona's for exactly 4 seconds, 3 seconds to play the song, 1 second to remove it from the song slot so I can put something more useful there. Honestly, I don't think theres a single situation in which I would play Rizlona's fire at the level I got it(54). There really isnt much you can raid at this level that this song will make or break. Add in the fact that there is no haste component makes this song plain useless IMO.
<br />

<br />
And the wind instrument mod? I got it for the same reason, to use to make singing invis song easier without having to pop in an instrument and also to raise the charm song MR debuff. However, the slot type as mentioned above is not easy to find a home on, most of what you find will worsen your stats overall. 
<br />

<br />
I ended up selling the aug back and reclaiming the points I spent.
<br />

<br />
If I were you, I'd save the points for the EC lute or for Call of the Muse later on(lvl 65). Or even for the magic based chant from North Ro(lvl 63 I think). All those would be much better use of hard earned adventure points.
<br />

<br />
